{"tid":1568072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[係時候要增加班廢佬成本」","createTime":"2019-09-14T08:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T08:18:41.000Z","uid":287547,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d89cd3ee1892adb4ff685ac88f27dbd717e210dc","tid":1568072,"uid":287547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:14:55.000Z","msg":"代朋友個朋友個親戚個老婆個老豆post, 已fc.<br />\n<br />\n佢老豆係已退休攞緊綜援住公屋既藍絲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n   班曱甴暴徒成9日搞亂曬個社會，搞死個經濟，一定要好好教訓佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n   不嬲平時都好得閒，最近係公園d 街方問我去唔去搵下錢去撕d 暴徒貼紙，100蚊次，又有錢搵又可以教訓曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 咁正我當然即場報左名。<br />\n    咁個日大約一點左右，我就跟班街方一齊出發啦。去到個度，成條街都係d暴徒貼既細紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇到到眼冤，我地大約撕左一個鐘左右就撕曬成條天橋既紙，好彩班暴徒蠢，全部痴埋一齊，一撕就成片撕曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 撕完成水成汗咁就去出糧啦。<br />\n   呢度我先最嬲既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,<br />\n   我跟大隊行到去一個偏偏地既涼亭度，明明個d只係辛苦費，佢地仲地扣起我50,話下次出來再出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都算啦。<br />\n   過多幾日之後，突然有政府人上來拎住張相來搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,話有人影到我收錢(實係d死曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 話懷疑我有其他收入，要我申報資產同收入來源，仲話唔排除cut我綜援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,我而家就問緊人點填份野，有可能今個月綜援都冇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死曱甴。各位街方要小心唔好俾人影到呀！！！<br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  你知啦，我地d支持警察既街方好多都唔得閒fc, 唔想因為我呢個而少左敢出來教訓曱甴既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n引申：以上只是代post, 不代表本人立場"},{"pid":"2422782780ab624beaaa0396b51d005b349dd174","tid":1568072,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:15:49.000Z","msg":"Agree"},{"pid":"d39dbdd05b0176a4654f9ae1ec395dedea01daa1","tid":1568072,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:16:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54d916cacaf4d4808780772dfa4ac825683c0641","tid":1568072,"uid":132106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:18:41.000Z","msg":"1999"}]}